com.gridgraph.structure

Class GridGraph.AnonymousGridGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.structure.GridGraph
      • com.gridgraph.structure.GridGraph.AnonymousGridGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AutoCloseable, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Graph, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.util.Host
    Enclosing class:
    GridGraph

    public static class GridGraph.AnonymousGridGraph
extends GridGraph
    Provides a unified way to construct a GridGraph for an application. With this instance, a GridGraph could be used in the client side without the needs to specifying details that're needed by a server application.
